manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Perfect Solution Virtuosa brings the vibes! This collection was intentionally created for every & any day; in the air, on a train, in the car, or simply at home, Virtuosa is the perfect solution to all your needs.

The Ultimate Carry-On Elevate your carry-on aesthetic with the Virtuosa Expandable Carry On. Featuring expansion, a TSA integrated lock, RightHeight handle, dual spinner wheels, and sleek leather-like accents, this case is the ultimate stylish addition!

Handle RightHeight handle system offers multiple 1-inch incremental height adjustments for a highly customized fit. Interior Organization The zippered storage compartment and a WetPak pocket and PU accented compression strap keep items organized making this carry-on your favorite travel companion. Dual Spinner Wheels 360° dual spinner wheels for effortless maneuverability on any surface.

How to Use the TSA Combination Lock Our TSA-approved combination locks are simple and easy to use, no key required! Use a ballpoint pen or other pointed object to press the small button located near the dials. With the button pressed in, set the dials to your desired code, and slide the button with the key hole towards to the dials to set. The code is now ready to use. The key hole is intended only for use by TSA agents, and no keys are included or required to use our TSA combination locks. The factory default code for new luggage is 0-0-0.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love at first sight
reviews.reviewText: I seen this on social media and had to have it. I have never had a hard suit case before so I am eager to see how it holds up. It does come with a warranty for samsonite. the wheels are super smooth which is important when moving about the airport.. The locks are an included bonus built into the case and if you want to bring back souvenirs that not a problem because the bag can expand. I am known for bringing back more than I left with. Love this case

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Classy 21" Carry-on Luggage
reviews.reviewText: I like the color kind of midnight blue with brown leather accent around top. The case material is somewhat like a hard plastic. It has a custom adjustment telescopic handle that can be raised or lowered an inch at a time. This luggage is expandable (width) to about 1 inch. I measured it to be approximately 15 x 10 x 21 in. case dimensions (excluding wheels in height). I also weighed the luggage to be about 7.7 pounds (empty weight) - it is light which i really like. It has 4 dual spinner wheels one for each corner that makes this luggage "glide" with a little push. It also has a "TSA approved" locking mechanism. I googled on how to set your personal combination - very easy to set it up. Opening the luggage you will see an ample room for your belongings - it has a lot of pockets and all zippers are all "fine-tooth" and closes smooth and flushed. Has a wet pack pocket for your toiletries. And there's more.... it has a 10 year manufacturer's warranty. I had Samsonites before and it seems they are "indestructible" they last a long time with regular handling. I wished they could have put a protective rib on the underside when you lay it down to open the luggage - but not a deal breaker for me. I consider this luggage very classy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gorgeous, fully functional suitcase
reviews.reviewText: I’ve ordered my fair share of Amazon suitcases, and maybe it’s obvious, but you get what you pay for. I love the Samsonite brand and have had several over the years. The quality is obvious from first glance and to every detail. This suitcase comes with a 10-year warranty, just to back that up.In terms of features, the hard shell is really strong and solid, even though the suitcase is very lightweight. The spinner wheels glide effortlessly and spin easily in every direction. The handle is adjustable to many different heights so you can customize it for you. The inside has a newer design compression strap that is really interesting. And also the standard zip closure side also features a built in waterproof toiletry section. Super convenient. The built in TSA lock and expandable zipper are also nice features. I can’t think of anything else I would want in a carry on suitcase.I also love the cream and brown design which looks really high end. I also ordered the matching Virtuosa backpack which coordinates beautifully.My only caution is that this suitcase is carry on sized for most US carriers but probably wouldn’t pass on international carriers or airlines that are super strict—with wheels it’s 23” tall. So if you’re team carry on only and hate a gate check, just be certain the measurements will work for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good Quality Carry-On
reviews.reviewText: This Virtuoso Samsonite carryon is a nice bag. The wheels spin easily in all directions, and the construction gives you the benefits of hard-sided luggage (more resistant to rips and tears) while retaining some of the benefits of soft-sided luggage (it has the ability to expand, thanks to a zipper in the middle).The inside of the bag is lined, and it has zippered compartments for small (and liquid) items. The compartments also serve to divide the two sides of the luggage. There are the usual straps so you can secure your items.In general, I am pleased. Since this is an early example of the Virtuosa line, it's not clear whether you will be able to find other bags to match this one. The other big question is that of price. Some places charge double what I have seen it at others. So be sure to shop around before buying it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing Carry On!! It looks Beautiful!!
reviews.reviewText: This is an amazing Luggage piece! It looks stunning!!The nice navy blue goes really well together with the brown piece of leather going across. The suitcase is nice and hard making it nice and sturdy so that it can get your luggage safely to its destination!! The entire suitcase is really nice and the attention to detail is great! The inside lining is very nice, the zippers are great, and I love the lock that it comes with to ensure your luggage is safe! The wheels are great as well, each wheel having the double-sided wheels!!All in all, this is a great piece of luggage from samsonite!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Where are we going?
reviews.reviewText: Well I broke my rule with this one! I was firm believer in only getting luggage in a dark color. I know I will need to pack my magic erasers, but I simply could not resist the elegant and upscale look of this luggage. The tan color is beautiful.It arrives locked so know the code is 000 to unlock. It would be nice if the tag describing it was hung on the outside of the bag, instead of safely locked away! Lol! We had to look up the item on amazon to learn how to get into it. But... this is my first piece of luggage with a built in lock system. Perhaps they all arrive this way?The wheels seem to be secure and sturdy. Glides effortlessly.The inside is roomy with the added expander option. There is a removable plastic pocket for toiletries.Overall we are pleased with it. I have never had a hard case suitcase before and am curious if I will miss the outside pockets. I think for short getaways this will be perfect.Time to book that trip!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing! Sturdy, ample storage and options!
reviews.reviewText: The Samsonite Virtuosa Hardside Expandable Luggage in Pine Green, particularly the 21-Inch carry-on, stands out for its combination of style and functionality. The distinctive color adds a touch of elegance, making it easy to spot among luggage. The durable hardside construction ensures that your belongings remain well-protected during travel, while the expandable feature provides flexibility for packing. The spinner wheels contribute to smooth maneuverability, reducing the hassle of navigating busy airports or city streets. With Samsonite's reputation for quality, this luggage piece offers a reliable and stylish travel companion for those seeking both durability and aesthetic appeal in their luggage.
